    <item>
      <title>流水无痕</title>
      <link>https://mowenpan.xyz/post/2019/09/16/b29c5031-eb49-11ea-ab6b-11c32936d76e</link>
      <guid>https://mowenpan.xyz/post/2019/09/16/b29c5031-eb49-11ea-ab6b-11c32936d76e</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2019 03:56:30 GMT</pubDate>
      
        
        
      <description>&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; class=&quot;aplayer-secondary-style-marker&quot; href=&quot;\assets\css\APlayer.min.css&quot;&gt;&lt;script src=&quot;\assets\js\APlayer.min.js&quot; cla</description>
        
      
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><blockquote><p>天已暮，乌鹊南飞去<br>梦醒处，流水不留痕</p></blockquote><p>乘着木筏带大海上飘荡<br>四周望不见大陆<br>鲸鱼放起冲天的水柱<br>光变得五彩斑斓，迷乱、沉沦<br>透过指缝看见南十字星<br>它指引方向</p><blockquote><p>水光月光相互交融</p></blockquote><p>狂花缓绽，落叶从容<br>星之声<br>闭上眼静静聆听<br>光经过漫长的旅行<br>走过时间的轨迹<br>撒向渴望着她的生命</p><p>我纵身跃入海中<br>穿过海雪向深处堕落<br>肌肤被侵蚀<br>在眼中结成了翳<br>从此再无光明</p><p>海水沁入伤痕<br>痛楚让我清醒<br>每一寸肌肤在感受着水的流动<br>失去知觉被冲上沙滩<br> 当我醒来又是风平浪静</p><blockquote><p>岁月不居，时节如流</p></blockquote>]]></content:encoded>
      
      
