    <item>
      <title>雨箭</title>
      <link>https://mowenpan.xyz/post/2019/09/02/b29c5035-eb49-11ea-ab6b-11c32936d76e</link>
      <guid>https://mowenpan.xyz/post/2019/09/02/b29c5035-eb49-11ea-ab6b-11c32936d76e</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2019 13:39:54 GMT</pubDate>
      
        
        
      <description>&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; class=&quot;aplayer-secondary-style-marker&quot; href=&quot;\assets\css\APlayer.min.css&quot;&gt;&lt;script src=&quot;\assets\js\APlayer.min.js&quot; cla</description>
        
      
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><blockquote><p>黯然消魂者，惟别而已矣。</p></blockquote><p>似乎离别的日子总是要下点雨<br>风也是寒冷刺骨<br>再风的助力下<br>雨箭似要锥进离人的心<br>本就滴血的两颗心<br>此时已血涌如潮</p><blockquote><p>杨柳岸，晓风残月。</p></blockquote><p>一去经年，虚设这良辰好景<br>路人来往匆匆<br>泥泞的道路，浸湿的裤脚<br>寒蝉鸣泣，夏蛙啜声<br>此处待回转</p>]]></content:encoded>
      
      
