    <item>
      <title>长歌一曲</title>
      <link>https://mowenpan.xyz/post/2019/08/31/b29c5034-eb49-11ea-ab6b-11c32936d76e</link>
      <guid>https://mowenpan.xyz/post/2019/08/31/b29c5034-eb49-11ea-ab6b-11c32936d76e</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2019 06:52:14 GMT</pubDate>
      
        
        
      <description>&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; class=&quot;aplayer-secondary-style-marker&quot; href=&quot;\assets\css\APlayer.min.css&quot;&gt;&lt;script src=&quot;\assets\js\APlayer.min.js&quot; cla</description>
        
      
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><blockquote><p>长歌一曲<br>好风，好梦，好歌，好义气</p></blockquote><p>禁锢<br>紧闭门窗<br>我用黑布遮挡住光</p><p>蜷缩<br>默不作声<br>心脏在律动</p><p>聆听<br>长歌当哭<br>春风融化经年冻雪</p><blockquote><p>早知穷达有命<br>恨不十年读书</p></blockquote><p>读经史子集<br>习四书五经<br>未尝得阳春白雪</p><p>览古今<br>学中外<br>惊觉千篇一律</p><p>把酒来<br>将欲饮<br>却得知音何方</p><p>高山不见流水<br>草枯，木腐<br>广陵散再奏待何人</p><blockquote><p>君应有语，渺万里层云；<br>千山暮雪，只影向谁去？</p></blockquote><p>白山茶开了<br>循环往复<br>终究跳不出轮回</p><p>红色的芍药也开了<br>风姿绰约，群芳失色<br>看尽沧海桑田</p><blockquote><p>念桥边红药，年年知为谁生</p></blockquote><p>西行东渡<br>哪一个不是修罗场<br>修罗刀下谁堪怜</p><p>在朝在野<br>谁不曾壮志激昂<br>名利场中皆刍狗</p><blockquote><p>我本西方一衲子</p></blockquote><p>青灯黄卷<br>沙门中谁个曾悟了<br>出家在家有何分别</p>]]></content:encoded>
      
      
